Microsoft Corp. (MSFT)  founder Bill Gates
ruled out returning to head the company or take on a full-time
role, the Age newspaper  reported .  Gates said he would focus fully on philanthropic work at
the  Bill & Melinda Gates Foundation  for the rest of his life,
the newspaper said on its website today. Gates said he is part-
time involved with Microsoft, including giving advice as
recently as this week, according to the report.  Microsoft, based in Redmond, Washington, is the worldâ€™s
